	This cute looking green dragon is full of character. &lsquo;Things are Looking Up&rsquo; dragon is a small green dragon with white dots on his body. He has large, boggle like eyes and large nostrils that seem out of proportion slightly, giving him a funny look. He has two small horns on his head and one on his nose, he also has his wings up on his back but they are closed together.&nbsp; He is lying on his belly and has a bewildered expression on his face. &lsquo;Things are Looking Up&rsquo; dragon is approximately 7cm long.</p>
